transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Uh sir Rahul baat kar raha tha IndiaMART se. Sir wo beech mein na ek customer ki meri thodi meeting lambi chali gayi thi.
Customer: Haan sir meri bhi meeting lambi chali hui hai. Aap subah baat kar kal 4 baje kar liyo aap.
Executive: 4 baje? Kal 4 baje sir?
Customer: Kal 4 baje. Kal kal 4 baje.
Executive: Theek hai sir main kal 4 baje ka. Agar subah agar rahega sir subah bhi kar sakta hu. Subah ka...
Customer: Subah nahi aap 4 baje kariyo. Kal 4 baje. Laptop jo chalata hai na bhai wo 4 baje aayega chutti se.
Executive: Achha.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Chaliye theek hai sir. Kal 4 baje connect karta hu.
Customer: Theek hai ji.
